title: Weird Al Yankovic - The complete discography
description:
All his albums, including:

"Weird Al" Yankovic [1983]
"Weird Al" Yankovic in 3-D [1984]
Dare to Be Stupid [1985]
Polka Party! [1986]
Even Worse [1988]
UHF [1989]
Off the Deep End [1992]
Alapalooza [1993]
Bad Hair Day [1996]
Running with Scissors [1999]
Poodle Hat [2003]
Straight Outta Lynwood 	[2006]

All of these are in AAC (m4a) format. This saves space, and the format is playable in most popular players, including Winamp and iTunes.

This is a reupload, some files were corrupted in the other version.
